<h2>Changed States</h2>

<ul>
	<li>
	When a sub-section is selected:
	<ul>
		<li>The active class gets added to it.</li>
		<li>The unordered list that is a part of it gets a class of open</li>
		<li>Expanded gets set to True</li>
		<li>Aria-hidden gets set to False</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li>
	When a sub-section is un-selected:
	<ul>
		<li>The active class gets removed from it.</li>
		<li>The unordered list that is a part of it has the open class removed</li>
		<li>Expanded gets set to False</li>
		<li>Aria-hidden gets set to True</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
</ul>
